Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是笹笹笹笹笹笹笹原學長！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:19:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  一副鴿子被槍打到了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  那個怎麼辦啊  我必須要說點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  今天天氣真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我到底在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  烏雲密佈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好深奧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這枚錢幣是閣下的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.41,0:19:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你特地給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:41.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這種事也是會發生的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我是說今天我碰巧忘帶錢包的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想潤潤喉嚨  恰好就經過了自動販賣機前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還在這裡撿到了錢幣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被上天眷顧的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我現在將要喝的飲料  是上天賜予的聖水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:10.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ambasa  一種乳性碳酸飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台自動販賣機…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這台自動販賣機居然不理會我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有著這個時代所罕見的膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欣賞！  那枚錢幣就賞給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學…學長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有根據
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我覺得我和學長之間的距離好像縮短了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  蜜瓜果汁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想告訴我什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長野原學姐可是厲害到被稱作無敵的強人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬  桂馬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起桂馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.83,0:22:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  浴室空出了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.78,0:22:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這月亮笹原學長也在看著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.87,0:22:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹原君你素質相當好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.77,0:22:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再和我姐姐一起練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.33,0:22:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次來教你必殺技吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.89,0:23:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不要擅自進來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.93,0:23:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在發呆想些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.07,0:23:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  不關你的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別害羞別害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  別管我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.20,0:24:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在沒有10円的時候才不會找錢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.23,0:25:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我  自動販賣機的法則
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.54,0:25:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的日常是第二十五話  敬請期待
